{"tid":1734721,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(線上遊戲)其實我覺得每個人需要帶嘅野係「盾」","createTime":"2019-11-18T11:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T11:40:34.000Z","uid":96561,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fe77085928a4378bf45adf2696c765ca310c944e","tid":1734721,"uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:39:36.000Z","msg":"盾，唔係單單用黎防禦<br />\n佢亦都係好好嘅壓制道具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打過機（dark soul)都知<br />\n<br />\n近距離嘅話：<br />\n你一個人比三，四個盾牌兵逼撚住嘅情況吓，你除咗走之外，就係攻擊，但之後就會比盾牌兵格檔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遠距離嘅話：<br />\n你嘅遠攻都會比盾牌檔晒（貫通系攻擊除外）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n咁盾牌嘅款式通常都係個幾味<br />\n木盾，鐵盾<br />\n<br />\n佢地亦都分長盾，方形盾，圓盾<br />\nP.s. Dark Soul嘅長盾兵好撚煩，次次都打到嬲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我分享吓我最鐘意用嘅0 level盾！<br />\n咁就係用完即棄嘅紙皮盾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料費低，易入手，輕，作用大！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n性價比係極高！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n將幾塊紙皮加埋一齊，個防禦力同硬度都有返咁上下！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n變相依家個選擇，一係就0裝走，一係就盾牌壓制。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攻略就分享完啦，有冇用就見人見智（推薦團體用），亦都希望各位成功，我就繼續玩我嘅dark soul，拜！"},{"pid":"910dc26105d2542087572352b5529f792ac4b2fd","tid":1734721,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:40:34.000Z","msg":"Twitter組24時keep住更新<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手retweet+ like + reply</span> <br />\n㩒入----&gt; <a